node.text:
does a bed count as a desk? is school now just a chat room filled with faces? these are confusing times. and the Impossible™️ Whopper makes things, well, a little more confusing. 

@impossible_foods

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Burger King on September 15, 2021 tagging @nelly. May be an image of 1 person and burger.

node.text:
i was like good gracious this meal is delicious. 🥵 get the Cornell Haynes Jr. meal featuring a Whopper sandwich with cheese and fries. just for the real ones out there, we’ve banned 120 artificial ingredients across our food menu. available for a limited time at BK #keepitrealmeals 

learn more at bk.com/realmeals. limited time only at participating U.S. Burger King® restaurants.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Burger King on September 14, 2021 tagging @lilhuddy. May be an image of 1 person and text that says 'KING BURGER'.

node.text:
21st-century vampires 🧛🏻 might not sleep, but they do sip on real ingredients. get the Chase Hudson meal with a Ch’King and mozzarella sticks and see why banning 120 artificial ingredients across our food menu was a delicious decision. available for a limited time at BK 🖤 #keepitrealmeals 

learn more at bk.com/realmeals. limited time only at participating U.S. Burger King® restaurants.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Burger King on September 13, 2021 tagging @anitta, and @impossible_foods. May be an image of 1 person, sitting, burger and indoor.

node.text:
✨the Larissa Machado meal✨ now at BK for a limited time, featuring an Impossible™️ Whopper and fries. banning over 120 artificial ingredients across our food menu has never tasted this good #keepitrealmeals 

learn more at bk.com/realmeals. limited time only at participating U.S. Burger King® restaurants.
